\h BONUS \d

\uUSAGE\n
!bonus name

\uDESCRIPTION\n
Give another player bonus experience points for outstanding role-playing.
Provide as an argument the name of a character who has introduced themselves to you (via the "intro" command).

Note that you must be at least level 3 to use this command, and you may only give out a bonus once every 24 hours.

\uRULES\n
This command is for the express purpose of rewarding fellow players for outstanding role-playing; it may not be used under any other circumstances. Please be discriminating and sensible.
Misuse of this command is grounds for discipline up to and including banishment from CurryMUD.

\uSEE ALSO\n
intro, glossary, role-play, rules, stats
